{"itemid":358,"subject":"New Figures From Dark Sword","event":"Dark Sword has just released their long-awaited Tyrion Lannister miniature, previewed below.  The figure is available in both 28mm and 54mm scales, unpainted.  The new Theon Greyjoy figure and a couple of cool hedge knights sclupted by Jeff Grace have also been added to the 29mm range, along with lots of new additions from Dark Sword's other lines.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://pics.livejournal.com/grrm/pic/0003ayx2/\"><img src=\"http://pics.livejournal.com/grrm/pic/0003ayx2/s320x240\" width=\"187\" height=\"240\" border='0'/></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://pics.livejournal.com/grrm/pic/0005b7r4/\"><img src=\"http://pics.livejournal.com/grrm/pic/0005b7r4/s320x240\" width=\"135\" height=\"240\" border='0'/></a>\r\n\r\nTo order, visit Dark Sword's online store at http://darkswordminiatures.com/store.html\r\n\r\nThey take PayPal now as well.","ditemid":91734,"eventtime":"2009-06-11 12:08:00","props":{"personifi_word_count":81,"taglist":"miniatures, dark sword","current_moodid":109,"opt_screening":"F","commentalter":1248207496,"personifi_tags":"19:100,9:100,nterms:yes"},"can_comment":0,"logtime":"2009-06-11 18:14:44","anum":86,"url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/91734.html","event_timestamp":1244722080,"reply_count":18,"comments":[{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/91734.html?replyto=6386262","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/91734.html?thread=6386262#t6386262","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/91734.html?thread=6386262#t6386262","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/91734.html?thread=6386262#t6386262","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"mishmarlayla","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://mishmarlayla.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":6386262,"talki